column6:
为自身附加<UIForeground>F201F4</UIForeground><UIGlow>F201F5</UIGlow>肉斩骨断<UIGlow>01</UIGlow><UIForeground>01</UIForeground>状态
<UIForeground>F201F4</UIForeground><UIGlow>F201F5</UIGlow>肉斩骨断<UIGlow>01</UIGlow><UIForeground>01</UIForeground>持续时间内受到的伤害越高，一击的威力越高
<UIForeground>F201F8</UIForeground><UIGlow>F201F9</UIGlow>持续时间：<UIGlow>01</UIGlow><UIForeground>01</UIForeground>15秒
<UIForeground>F201F4</UIForeground><UIGlow>F201F5</UIGlow>狙击<UIGlow>01</UIGlow><UIForeground>01</UIForeground>的效果量提高到30%，并且攻击必定命中
<UIForeground>F201F4</UIForeground><UIGlow>F201F5</UIGlow>狙击<UIGlow>01</UIGlow><UIForeground>01</UIForeground>的效果量提高到50%，并且攻击必定命中
居合斩的威力提高到500，即死的几率提高到10%
歌吟的效果量会随吟游诗人的辅助职业等级提升而提升
可以开启迷宫中上锁的门
发动炮击时，有5%的几率即死目标

<UIForeground>F201F4</UIForeground><UIGlow>F201F5</UIGlow>战斗之铃<UIGlow>01</UIGlow><UIForeground>01</UIForeground>的效果量提高至5%
<UIForeground>F201F4</UIForeground><UIGlow>F201F5</UIGlow>休憩之铃<UIGlow>01</UIGlow><UIForeground>01</UIForeground>的恢复力提高至3000
